-- Finavera in ‘Advanced’ Discussions With Four Potential Buyers
-- B y   T i n a   D a v i s
-- 2012-10-05T12:36:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-05/finavera-in-advanced-discussions-with-four-potential-buyers.html
Finavera Wind Energy Inc. (FVR) , a
Vancouver-based wind-farm developer, said it’s in talks with
four potential bidders and initial offers are expected soon.  In addition, a “number of new entrants” have signed non-
disclosure agreements and are reviewing the company’s
financials, Finavera Wind said in a statement today.  The company rose 40 percent on Oct. 1 after annoucing it
was in talks with three potential buyers and had hired Capital
West Partners LLC to review offers.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tina Davis at 
 tinadavis@bloomberg.net  